<h6>Tarceva<sup>®</sup> (erlotinib) tablets</h6>
<h1>A therapeutic advance in the treatment of 2nd line NSCLC and 1st line pancreatic cancer</h1>
<p>Tarceva monotherapy is indicated for the treatment of patients with locally advanced or metastatic non-small cell lung cancer after failure of at least one prior chemotherapy regimen.  Tarceva is also approved for the first-line treatment of  locally advanced, unresectable or metastatic pancreatic cancer in combination with gemcitabine (chemotherapy).</p>
